  m_Name: Email_Day01_01
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::EmailData
  senderName: Content Corp. HR
  senderAddress: hr@content-corp.net
  subject: Welcome to the team
  body: 'Dear Moderator,


    Welcome aboard. You have been assigned to the Content
    Review Division, Day Shift.


    Your task is straightforward: review flagged
    posts and remove anything that violates our Community Standards (spam, profanity,
    abuse). Approve everything else.


    You are helping make the internet a cleaner
    place. We appreciate your service.


    Best regards,

    HR Department

    Content
    Corp.'
  showOnDay: 1
